text:
<!here> *IS TODAY’S ACTIVITY*

*LinkedIn Post Challenge: My 10 Academy Story*

It's my hope that we have built our LinkedIn profiles during the career session. Today we are going to makes a post!:dancer:
• Go to your LinkedIn timeline (account) and share a post about your 10 Academy experience attaching the poster provided below(Choose one of our favorite ) . LinkedIn allows you to use a lot more words so feel free to pour your heart out with words.
• After posting, take the *`screenshot`* and the *`link`* to your post…share it on *all-community slack channel*. Follow other trainees on LinkedIn and like their posts to build a following.
• *NOTE: To make you post catchy, it is important to*
    ◦ Start your post with a *‘HOOK’ line (attention grabber) - e.g This is my 10 Academy story! A story of my life at 10 Academy! Unforgettable experience at 10 Academy!*
    ◦ Tag 10 Academy handle by using *(*@ 10 *Academy)* -make sure it turns blue when u tag.
    ◦ Speak your heart, don't worry much about perfection -you can always edit later. Attach the poster below.
